{"tid":2446175,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事］Staycation 酒店靈異事件","createTime":"2021-03-14T08:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T12:57:22.000Z","uid":128638,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dd87cb3c91c1391f5db203e616ca182311b3b5b8","tid":2446175,"uid":128638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴日同女友訂咗灣X國際 諗住staycation...點知我哋掛住行街睇戲，最後搞到5點鐘先去 check-in，搞完手續上到房太急，我哋兩個都唔記得敲門就入房...一入到去間房有陣臭味，天花板又霉燈光又暗，但都不以為意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSettle 好我哋就叫 Foodpanda 食，等等下外賣諗住開個電視睇下，故事去到呢度都正正常常。外賣到咗之後我就熄電視落 Lobby 拎外賣，食飯其間我哋都係睇iPad，冇再開過個電視睇<br />\n<br />\n食到一半時突然個電視第自己開咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同女友都以為係機件問題，都冇咩點理，熄咗佢繼續食。但其實我隱約係窗倒影到見到有團黑影...廁所門又自己打開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過多10分鐘，個電視第二次自己開....今次我同女友呆咗，順手又熄翻佢。因為今次個電視唔係開咗咁簡單，佢係自己轉緊台搵緊channel 同自已較緊音量，我哋嚇到即刻熄咗佢，同埋將個 Remote 放係身邊，確保佢唔會再自己開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知.....個電視機好似shot shot 地咁不停自己開，跳制，忽然好大聲....我大大聲講 你唔好再㩒啦吓，諗住定一定驚，睇下我啲陽氣震住啲污糟野，然後....我哋再狂㩒個熄機制，佢無反應.....今次電視機熄都熄唔到....女友嚇到即刻熄左個總制，我哋都驚到拿拿淋汁野退房<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n退房個時好心同酒店啲人講聲，電視機好似有啲問題，佢哋都不以為意...純粹分享，大家以後揀酒店小心啲.....同埋真係記得入住前敲下門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a9f5cb30ee29de2948ae045a5ccb60784e21e9","tid":2446175,"uid":185460,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"試下射篤精落部電視度 用陽氣鎮一鎮佢"},{"pid":"6648a5be4f3f182675c2483fe2a31a9aece46a04","tid":2446175,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"你遲in咁冇計<br />\n酒店fo都盡量比哂啲正常房客人先 有問題嘅都會最後比"},{"pid":"ddb24e47b0e29a0bc2ddfedaa2c7a1b97434c837","tid":2446175,"uid":16041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"我都試過，半夜開電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔係香港"},{"pid":"bddedaa839599c893a37a35ae57bd7dd10ce04b9","tid":2446175,"uid":128638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a9f5cb30ee29de2948ae045a5ccb60784e21e9","tid":2446175,"uid":185460,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"試下射篤精落部電視度 用陽氣鎮一鎮佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到9都縮埋"},{"pid":"ee4a06a54937332daa372fd1f6189f7ab649409c","tid":2446175,"uid":199877,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"原來依家仲有人住酒店會敲門入房 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74158d17a4219035b10d113608e49bbfe9d25424","tid":2446175,"uid":128638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee4a06a54937332daa372fd1f6189f7ab649409c","tid":2446175,"uid":199877,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"原來依家仲有人住酒店會敲門入房 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2d5ca66fa57ae0fb9b5bb5706047607dac7cb9","tid":2446175,"uid":106026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"同佢講你呢隻廢鬼, 有三萬黑警有777有習總唔搞係要搞我, 正一廢物."},{"pid":"1d5050271828a10109015ed51be64e7aa95cfeb0","tid":2446175,"uid":83989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a2d5ca66fa57ae0fb9b5bb5706047607dac7cb9","tid":2446175,"uid":106026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021